<br>
A similar argument could be made about Mages not having mob disabling spells when other pet classes do that allow thier pets to &quot;tank&quot;:  Shaman: Turgor's Insects (slows mobs: 66%-75%), Enchanters: (Shiftless Deeds lvl:44--slows mobs: 65%), Necromancers: Darkness + Fear (no tanking required). <br>
<br>
