<br>
Rather than ask for mana regeneration, why not ask for lower casting costs?  Same difference.  Clerics might not get mana regeneration of any form but their buffs last for well over an hour.  Enchanter buffs last on the average of 15 minutes--so, if you do the math, you need to quadruple the mana cost of the enchanter buffs and compare that to the mana usage of the cleric buffs.<br>
<br>
